{"tid":1311740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣PPT：香港人被打不還手，是否是東亞病夫？","createTime":"2019-07-13T10:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T06:09:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":887,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"af158a5539c97c495cf59a35e83b15c1e104af18","tid":1311740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pttweb.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1562903866.A.49E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pttweb.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1562903866.A.49E&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=86ffc1c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pttweb.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1562903866.A.49E</a><br />\n<br />\n昨天晚上<br />\n香港地鐵站內親中派老人跟香港年青人發生衝突<br />\n有一名香港年青人還捱了親中派老人13次拳頭<br />\n另一名年青人還被親中派老人扭斷了手臂骨<br />\n但是那兩名年青人還堅持不還手，任由那個老人打<br />\n我去香港連登討論區了解一下情況，那兩名年青人不還手的原因<br />\n是因為香港人一直喜愛和平<br />\n他們希望堅持以和平和反對武力的方式感化親中派人士<br />\n並認為就算失去了手臂但這樣就可以讓世界各地人都同情香港人<br />\n認為還手的話就代表自己也使用了武力，跟親中派老人沒分別<br />\n<br />\n昨天兩名被打被扭斷手臂的年青人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/MuDY69D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuDY69D.gif&h=b3def13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心想。。。這根本是愚蠢好嗎＝ ＝<br />\n我是很支持香港年青人，但這樣被人毒打仍不還手根本只是東亞病夫＝ ＝"},{"pid":"a3802b4abeb14f6f49898cf0930b8b957f52edfd","tid":1311740,"uid":266343,"like":222,"dislike":1,"score":221,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"打斷手係另一晚 一個伯伯黎"},{"pid":"434dd98228c358c4d57f1caa5711625f123a7baf","tid":1311740,"uid":143499,"like":260,"dislike":29,"score":231,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"台灣五毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分化反抗勢力"},{"pid":"ce8f33b7f06dde8116e57a2c882cd09c3834df34","tid":1311740,"uid":238551,"like":259,"dislike":15,"score":244,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5d84b05cd40eea30405b22987c4b13737401562","tid":1311740,"uid":4050,"like":18,"dislike":6,